launching RVIZ
Step 0: Open a new terminal
cd ~/ros2_ws
source install/setup.bash

Step 1: Check that ROS sees your package
ros2 pkg list | grep my_robot_description

Step 2: Launch RViz
ros2 launch my_robot_description display.launch.py

